<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Bid Accepted</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #4CAF50;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
        }
        .content {
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px;
        }
        .transaction-details {
            background-color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-left: 4px solid #4CAF50;
        }
        .final-amount {
            font-size: 24px;
            color: #4CAF50;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .next-steps {
            background-color: #e8f5e8;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
            color: #666;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>✅ Your Bid Has Been Accepted! ✅</h1>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
        <h2>Hello {{buyerName}},</h2>
        
        <p>Excellent news! The seller has accepted your bid and the transaction is now confirmed!</p>
        
        <div class="transaction-details">
            <h3>Transaction Details:</h3>
            <p><strong>Item:</strong> {{auctionTitle}}</p>
            <p><strong>Auction ID:</strong> #{{auctionId}}</p>
            <p><strong>Seller:</strong> {{sellerName}}</p>
            <p><strong>Transaction Date:</strong> {{transactionDate}}</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="final-amount">
            Final Amount: ${{finalAmount}}
        </div>
        
        <div class="next-steps">
            <h3>What's Next?</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>You will receive an invoice via email within the next few minutes</li>
                <li>Please arrange payment and delivery details with the seller</li>
                <li>Keep this email as confirmation of your purchase</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        
        <p>Congratulations on your successful purchase! If you have any questions about this transaction, please don't hesitate to contact our support team.</p>
        
        <p>Thank you for using AuctionBid!</p>
        
        <p>Best regards,<br>
        The AuctionBid Team</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
        <p>This is an automated confirmation from AuctionBid Platform</p>
        <p>For support, please visit our help center or contact us directly</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
